text: György Snell (8 March 1949 - 26 Febraury 2021) was a Hungarian auxiliary bishop Roman Catholic bishop. He became a priest in 1972. He was auxiliary bishop of Pudentiana and as auxiliary bishop of the Roman Catholic Archdiocese of Esztergom-Budapest from 2014 until his death in 2021. Snell died on 26 February 2021, aged 71.György Snell ==References== Category:1949 births Category:2021 deaths Category:Hungarian Roman Catholic bishops Category:People from Budapest
